{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"报捷的诗篇","authors":["白玉明"],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":3,"day":20}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"报捷的诗篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京电碳厂工人　白玉明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉火，喷吐着鏖战的烈焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热浪，象大潮在心海里翻卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸烂“四人帮”的枷锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱奋斗在火红的车间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓风机高唱欢快的歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大汽锤亮开嗓门直喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不干谁干？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快去夺取灿烂的明天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司锤的姑娘巧手掀动千声雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌钳的小伙茧手追赶万道闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为共产主义大厦锻钢梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“铁人”和咱同在炉前挥大汗……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滴滴汗水写成报捷的诗篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如霞的喜报飞向华主席身边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间里一排排赤热的锻件，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是中国工人的火红肝胆！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}